9. Internet Down / Offline Operation

A well-designed RabbitOS architecture should degrade gracefully offline.

Fully Local Mode

Possible features:

local AI assistant

local telemetry

local dashboards

cached workflows

encrypted archives


No cloud required.


---

Offline Networking

Possible using:

mesh WiFi

LoRa

BLE relays

local MQTT brokers


This allows limited local communication without internet.


---

Delayed Synchronization

When internet returns:

queued packets upload

blockchain anchors sync

backups resume


10. Homomorphic Encryption Placement

HE is usually NOT run on tiny RF devices directly because it is computationally expensive.

Better placement:

edge server

workstation

cloud node


Tiny nodes instead use:

AES

Ed25519

SHA-256


HE workloads typically happen later in the pipeline.

